                        aspect.applyAdvice(proxy, method, args);
                    }
                    // Invoke the target method
                    return method.invoke(target, args);
                });
    }
}
```

In this example, the `CustomProxyFactory` class provides a method to create a dynamic proxy object for a target bean. The proxy object applies advices from the provided aspects before invoking the target method.

